<voice_0x0100105E><se_def>*: Ahem, ahem!
Sorry, just a bit of catarrh!

<voice_0x0100105F><se_def>*: Howzit? Welcome to Chateau Felix!
Residence of the great sabrecat father,
Master Felix!

<voice_0x01001060><se_def>*: My name's Tom.
I'm Master Felix's helper.
Are you here to see him?

<voice_0x01001061><se_def>Tom: Ahem!?
Then what are you doing here!?
You better scat now now!
<voice_0x01001063><se_def>Tom: Ahem! Excuse me!
<voice_0x01001064><se_def>Tom: But Master Felix is a busy man! He hasn't got time to meet any old thing the cat dragged in!

<voice_0x01001065><se_def>Tom: I'll have to ask you some questions.
If you can prove you're a top cat,
I'll let you in just now.
<voice_0x01001066><se_def>Tom: Question number one!

<voice_0x01001067><se_def>Tom: It's late and it's raining cats and dogs.
You're hurrying home, when you hear a little kitten meowing. It's right soaking wet.

<voice_0x01001068><se_def>Tom: But everyone in your house really hates cats.
So, what do you do with the kitten?
<voice_0x01001069><se_def>Tom: AHEM!

1 Move it to a sheltered place out of the rain.
2 Take it home and ask your family to let it stay.

<voice_0x0100106D><se_def>Tom: Question number two!

<voice_0x0100106E><se_def>Tom: You're the King's servant.
You go out hunting with the King,
but you don't manage to find any prey.

<voice_0x0100106F><se_def>Tom: Then you find a tiger in a trap in the woods!
The King is some way off and hasn't noticed the tiger yet.
<voice_0x01001070><se_def>Tom: So, what do you do?
<voice_0x01001072><se_def>Tom: AHEM!

0 Kill the tiger and then show it to the King.
1 Let the tiger live but show it to the King.
2 Free the tiger from the trap and let it go.

<voice_0x01001073><se_def>Tom: And question number three!
<voice_0x01001074><se_def>Tom: You are an explorer. Along your travels you're attacked by a great sabrecat.
<voice_0x01001075><se_def>Tom: You manage to overpower the cat, but it looks at you as if it wants to become your friend and travel with you.
<voice_0x01001071><se_def>Tom: So, what do you do?
<voice_0x0100105E><se_def>Tom: AHEM!

0 Deliver the finishing blow.
1 Leave without it.
2 Let the great sabrecat join you on your travels.

<voice_0x01001076><se_def>Tom: And now to let the cat out of the bag!
Let's see how you did!
<voice_0x01001077><se_def>Tom: I'm sorry, but you're not the kind of person Master Felix has the time to meet.
<voice_0x01001078><se_def>Tom: I can't let you in to see him meow. Sorry.
<voice_0x01001079><se_def>Tom: If you really want to see him, have another go at my test.

<voice_0x0100107A><se_def>Tom: Purrrfect!
You've proved that you're the cat's whiskers,
a real hip-cat!

<voice_0x0100107B><se_def>Tom: Ahem!
You have permission to see Master Felix.
You can go in.
<voice_0x0100105E><se_def>Tom: Ahem!

<voice_0x0100107C><se_def>Tom: Howzit!?
You want to try my test again?

<voice_0x01001062><se_def>Tom: No!? Suffering cats!
If you've got nothing to do here you better scat now now!
<voice_0x0100107D><se_def>Tom: Ahem! Okay! Here we go!
